\item $1$ minuyxTige $80$ rUpAyigaLanunx eNisa takakxMthA obabx sarAPanu $10$ lakaSx rUpAyigaLanunx eSuTx hotitxge eNisAyxnu? \hfill $208$ GaMTe $20$ minUyxTf.

